{"name": "Smith Persist MIPS Cycling Helmet - Unisex", "categories": ["Home", "All", "Cycling", "Bike helmets and body armour", "Bike helmets", "Persist MIPS Cycling Helmet"], "description": "They say cool heads prevail, they probably regularly crush their PRs too. With 21 strategically placed vents the Persist helmet helps keep you cool when you put the hammer down.MIPS\u00ae technology (Multi-directional Impact Protection System) reduces rotational forces in an oblique impact. An inner shell sandwiched between the foam and the padding reduces the rotational torque on the skull.AirEvac\u2122 system pulls warm air away from your sunglasses for reduced fogging.Pass-through channels to store glasses on the front.21 vents.Quick drying liner wicks away moisture.VaporFit\u2122 dial adjustment system offers 270-degrees fit adjustment for dialling in the perfect fit.", "product_code": "6012-468", "tech_specs": {"Weight": ["300g (Medium)"], "Ideal for": ["Sport road cycling", "Cycle commuting", "Cycle touring", "Gravel riding"], "Construction\n\nMicroshell helmets are made of a thin polymer sheet over a foam liner; Hardshell helmets have a hard polymer outer shell and a foam liner; when the liner is being bonded to the outer shell during the manufacturing process, it is Molded in the shell.": ["Molded in the shell"], "Shell material": ["Polycarbonate"], "Fit system": ["Adjustable dial"], "Inner material": ["EPS (expanded polystyrene)"], "Circumference\n\nThe internal circumference determines the size head that the helmet will fit.": ["51-55cm (Black Cement Small)", "55-59cm (Black Cement Medium)", "59-62cm (Black Cement Large)", "61-65cm (Black Cement X-Large)"], "Vents": ["Yes"], "Approved for\n\nMost helmets are tested and certified for a specific sport. Some helmets are approved for multi-sports, but only after passing the safety tests for both sports (i.e., snowsports and cycling).": ["Cycling"], "Safety rating\n\nCetification is established by a variety of governing bo